	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=66620><span id= >Slein</span></a><br><span id=notbold>234 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [2.79]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>That cannot be correct.&nbsp;&nbsp;You will never hit for less than your damage bonus unless on a ripost (no damage bonus) or offhand attack (dmg bonus is primary hand only).  Just think of damage bonus as whats added onto the end of your swing after passing through all of the other mods.  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Ok, I'll shut up now.<br><br>Slein Jinn<br>Dread Lord on everyone's least favorite server, E'ci<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=325772" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=325772</a></td></tr>
